================================================================================
 MUI MCC LayGroup class - ChangeLog
================================================================================

=== V19.3 RELEASE ==============================================================

2008-03-17   rmais96

   * Fix offset "centered" value bug
   * Extend values for space [0, 24] and offset [0, 32]

2008-03-16   rmais96

   * Replace image for preference class
   * Add new images for samples and demo

2008-03-15   rmais96

   * Add makefile for bruch2c tool
   * Enhance makefiles for catalogs modification
   * Make french catalog for preferences class
   * Add localization (only required for preferences class)

2008-03-13   rmais96

   * Remove useless and undocumented SleepWindow attribute

2008-03-08   rmais96

   * Rework preferences class for MorphOS/MUI4

2008-03-03   rmais96

   * Add makefiles
   * Port library from mccheader to mccinit

=== V19.2 RELEASE ==============================================================

2008-02-27   rmais96

   * Save 19.2 legacy Amiga m68k version from Alessandro Zummo

